{"id":"trellisworld","title":"TRELLISWorld: Training-Free World Generation from Object Generators","venue":"arXiv 2025","task":"general-scene-generation","summary":"Repurposes object generators as modular 3D tiles for scalable training-free scene synthesis.","paper":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2510.23880"}
