{"id":"bolt3d","title":"Bolt3D: Generating 3D Scenes in Seconds","venue":"ICCV 2025","task":"single-image-to-scene","summary":"A latent diffusion model that directly samples a 3D scene from one or more images in a few seconds.","paper":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2503.14445"}
