{"id":"mess","title":"MeSS: City Mesh-Guided Outdoor Scene Generation with Cross-View Consistent Diffusion","venue":"arXiv 2025","task":"outdoor-urban","summary":"Uses city meshes as geometric priors and diffusion-based view synthesis to create large realistic outdoor scenes.","paper":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2508.15169","domain":["outdoor-urban"]}
